quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  33,28,"Yewe muhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Bwira abagore bawe uti “Niba mwifuza ubuzima bw’iyi si n’imitako yayo, nimuze mbakorere ibyo mwifuza maze mbasende, dutane ku neza.”"
  33,29,"“Ariko niba mushaka (kwishimirwa na) Allah n’intumwa ye ndetse (munashaka) n’ubuturo bw’imperuka (Ijuru), mu by’ukuri (mumenye ko) Allah yateguriye ibihembo bihambaye abakora ibyiza muri mwe.”"
  33,30,"Yemwe bagore b’Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Muri mwe uzakora icyaha cy’urukozasoni mu buryo bugaragara, ibihano bye bizikuba kabiri, kandi ibyo kuri Allah biroroshye"
  33,31,"Kandi muri mwe uzumvira Allah n’intumwa ye akanakora ibikorwa byiza, tuzamugororera ibihembo byikubye kabiri, kandi (ku mperuka) twanamuteguriye amafunguro meza"
  33,32,"Yemwe bagore b’Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Ntabwo mumeze nk’abandi bagore basanzwe. Niba mutinya (Allah) muramenye ntimukoroshye amajwi (yanyu, igihe muvugana n’abandi bagabo), kugira ngo ufite uburwayi mu mutima atabifuza; ahubwo mujye muvuga mukoresheje imvugo ziboneye"
  33,33,"Mujye munaguma mu ngo zanyu kandi ntimukagaragaze imitako yanyu nk’uko abagore bo mu bihe by’ubujiji babikoraga. Mujye muhozaho iswala, mutange amaturo kandi mwumvire Allah n’Intumwa ye. Mu by’ukuri yemwe bantu bo mu rugo (rw’Intumwa)! Allah arashaka kubakuriraho ibibi n’ibyaha ndetse no kubasukura byimazeyo"
  33,34,"Munazirikane amagambo ya Allah n’amagambo y’Intumwa bisomerwa mu ngo zanyu. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Ugenzabuhoro, Umumenyi uhebuje"